做一个简单的测试: 创建两个非常简单的java文件, 执行如下指令:
D:\core\git2018\ilucky-java-test\ilucky-test-jvm\src\main\java>javac com/ilucky/test/jvm/classloader/one/*.java

D:\core\git2018\ilucky-java-test\ilucky-test-jvm\src\main\java>java com/ilucky/test/jvm/classloader/one/MyClassLoaderTest
I am in App ClassLoader


将MyClassLoaderTest中打印的内容调整为: System.out.println("I am in BootStrap ClassLoader");
将此java文件拷贝到E:\com\ilucky\test\jvm\classloader\one目录下, 执行javac指令:
E:\com\ilucky\test\jvm\classloader\one>javac MyClassLoader.java
同时将原来com/ilucky/test/jvm/classloader/one目录下的MyClassLoaderTest.class文件删除

继续执行如下指令:
D:\core\git2018\ilucky-java-test\ilucky-test-jvm\src\main\java>java com/ilucky/test/jvm/classloader/one/MyClassLoaderTest
Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: com/ilucky/test/jvm/classloader/one/MyClassLoader
        at com.ilucky.test.jvm.classloader.one.MyClassLoaderTest.main(MyClassLoaderTest.java:10)
Caused by: java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: com.ilucky.test.jvm.classloader.one.MyClassLoader
        at java.net.URLClassLoader.findClass(URLClassLoader.java:381)
        at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(ClassLoader.java:424)
        at sun.misc.Launcher$AppClassLoader.loadClass(Launcher.java:331)
        at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(ClassLoader.java:357)
        ... 1 more

D:\core\git2018\ilucky-java-test\ilucky-test-jvm\src\main\java>


继续执行如下指令(注意-Xbootclasspath):
D:\core\git2018\ilucky-java-test\ilucky-test-jvm\src\main\java>java -Xbootclasspath/a:E:/ com/ilucky/test/jvm/classloader/one/MyClassLoaderTest
I am in BootStrap ClassLoader

D:\core\git2018\ilucky-java-test\ilucky-test-jvm\src\main\java>
